OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) has started an
OL,9,Finvestigation into complaints about
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police's previous
OL,11,Fcontact with Valdo Calocane and their
OL,12,Fhandling of the murder investigation
OL,13,Ffollowing the deaths of three people
OL,14,Fin Nottingham in June last year.
OL,16,Fwas stabbed alongside fellow
OL,17,FUniversity of Nottingham student, ,
OL,18,Fand school caretaker, by . Three more
OL,19,Fpeople were injured in the attack.
