OL,7,FThe IOPC's investigation follows a
OL,8,Fvoluntary referral by the force of
OL,9,Fcomplaints they have received from the
OL,10,Fvictims' families.
OL,12,FThe complaints allege there were flaws
OL,13,Fin the handling of the murder
OL,14,Finvestigation and missed opportunities
OL,15,Fby police to prevent the deaths.
