OL,7,FAllegations have also been made in
OL,8,Frespect of the non-execution of an
OL,9,Foutstanding warrant for Calocane's
OL,10,Farrest prior to the killings, and
OL,11,Fconcerns raised about Nottinghamshire
OL,12,FPolice's communication with the
OL,13,Ffamilies.
OL,15,FIOPC Director of Operations, Steve
OL,16,FNoonan, said: "Our sympathies are with
OL,17,Fthe families of Barnaby Webber, Grace
OL,18,FO'Malley-Kumar, and Ian Coates, and
OL,19,Feveryone else affected by the tragic
OL,20,Fevents which took place on June 13
OL,21,Flast year.
