OL,7,F"We have now decided to investigate
OL,8,Fcomplaints made about Nottinghamshire
OL,9,FPolice's involvement with Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane. Along with this we are
OL,11,Finvestigating the actions and
OL,12,Fdecisions of Leicestershire Police,
OL,13,Fwhich we announced last week."
OL,15,FOn Tuesday 23 January, on the grounds
OL,16,Fof diminished responsibility due to
OL,17,F"serious" mental illness.
