OL,7,FCalocane was diagnosed with paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenia in 2019. He'd been
OL,9,Fsectioned four times and was known to
OL,10,Frefuse medication, something the
OL,11,Fprosecution argued led to a further
OL,12,Fdecline in his mental health.
OL,14,FThe health secretary has now ordered a
OL,15,Freview into the mental health services
OL,16,Fat the NHS trust where he was treated.
